Ethereum on ARM Monitoring Extras
============================================

This meta-package installs and configures the monitoring stack for Ethereum on ARM.

Features
--------

- **Dependencies**: Installs `prometheus`, `grafana`, `prometheus-node-exporter`, `ethereum-metrics-exporter`, and `ethereum-validator-metrics-exporter`.
- **Configuration**:
  - **Apt Preferences**: Configures package pinning in `/etc/apt/preferences.d/`.
  - **Systemd**: Sets up systemd overrides or configurations in `/etc/systemd/system/`.
  - **UFW**: Configures firewall application rules for monitoring services in `/etc/ufw/applications.d/`.

Data Directories
----------------

This package does not store persistent data.

